   Construction and Facilities Management

   :MISSION STATEMENT:

                             jet.gif (615 bytes)

             Our mission is to acquire, develop, and maintain land and
   facilities to support the adminisration, training, and readiness of the
   California National Guard; and to develop     and enhance relationships
   to maximize the value of our facilities to our soldiers and the
   communities we serve.

